value.name: Fidelidade - Wikipedia
value.snippet: Fidelidade is a Portuguese insurance company that was established in the early 19th century and is headquartered in Lisbon. It is a subsidiary of Fosun International. Portuguese leader in the domestic market, the company focuses on providing life and non-life products for both individuals and companies.
